¶ Reminded of frailty ¶

41:28.053 --> 41:32.522
¶ I feel like a child tonight ¶

41:32.524 --> 41:34.924
¶ Let the broken, weak ¶

41:34.926 --> 41:37.494
¶ And war-torn souls ¶

41:37.496 --> 41:41.631
¶ Soon return to life ¶

41:41.633 --> 41:46.035
¶ Wait till the morning ¶

41:46.037 --> 41:50.039
¶ It is bound to come ¶

41:50.041 --> 41:56.579
¶ Wait for a sign tonight ¶

41:57.716 --> 42:02.552
¶ Fear lies by the fireside ¶

42:02.554 --> 42:06.756
¶ Don't mean
there ain't hope tonight ¶

42:06.758 --> 42:10.660
¶ Wait on the sun ¶

42:10.662 --> 42:14.964
¶ There's better days to come ¶

42:14.966 --> 42:19.602
¶ And though these questions
blow your mind ¶

42:19.604 --> 42:22.906
¶ Answers are not
bound by time... ¶

42:22.908 --> 42:24.107
Hey.

42:24.109 --> 42:25.775
Hey.

42:25.777 --> 42:28.028
Listen, I... I wanted

42:28.029 --> 42:30.280
to let you know, if you
ever need to talk...
It's okay.

42:30.282 --> 42:32.015
¶ There's better days
to come... ¶

42:32.017 --> 42:34.751
You need any company?
You want to go grab a bite?

42:34.753 --> 42:37.687
Thanks.

42:37.689 --> 42:39.589
There's someplace I got to be.

42:39.591 --> 42:41.624
Okay.

42:41.626 --> 42:43.760
Bye.
All right,
thanks, Jules.

